shape: sequence_diagram
style: {
  font-size: 24
}

User
Orchestrator
Proponent
Opponent
Judge
LLM

User -> Orchestrator: Start Debate (Topic, Config)
Orchestrator -> Proponent: Generate Argument
Proponent -> LLM: Request Generation
LLM --> Proponent: Return Argument
Proponent --> Orchestrator: Submit Argument

Orchestrator -> Opponent: Generate Counter-Argument
Opponent -> LLM: Request Generation
LLM --> Opponent: Return Counter-Argument
Opponent --> Orchestrator: Submit Counter-Argument

Orchestrator -> Judge: Evaluate Round
Judge -> LLM: Request Evaluation
LLM --> Judge: Return Score & Summary
Judge --> Orchestrator: Submit Evaluation

Orchestrator --> User: Return Debate Result
